ADDITIONAL TERMS - MAPFRE INTEGRATION
------------------------------------

This software is designed to interact with the MAPFRE InfoCol web portal. The
following terms apply when integrating with MAPFRE systems:

1. Credentials for MAPFRE InfoCol must never be hard-coded, shared or
   committed to version control. Use the OS keychain or encrypted local
   storage (see config/settings.yaml).

2. Personal data obtained from InfoCol (DNI, policy numbers, addresses) must
   be sanitized before being sent to any external AI service (Claude API).
   The sanitizer module (src/infocol/security.py) handles this automatically.

3. Compliance with RGPD/LOPD is mandatory. The user is responsible for
   informing their data protection officer about the use of this tool.

4. The MAPFRE brand assets (logo, colors, typography) included in this
   project are used for demonstration purposes only with the goal of
   presenting this software to MAPFRE. Production use requires explicit
   written authorization from MAPFRE S.A.
